data.description: Great opportunity to live in sought after Kriewald Place. Spacious open floor with high ceilings. Beautiful Arch walls with 9ft ceilings in main floor giving your space an elegant, grand feel. Kitchen has granite countertops with black/SS appliances. Gas stove, built in microwave & dishwasher & great counter space. Lots of natural lighting, gives home a cozy, comfortable atmosphere. Stairway has mid landing, Spacious bedrooms. Master Extended double vanity with sep. tub tile backsplash & shower. 1/2 bath with pedestal vanity. Relax your evenings in the transformed landscaping. Back patio has sky covers and rock landscaping. A must see to appreciate.
